about.summary: Provides number-theoretic functions for factorization, prime  numbers, twin primes, primitive roots, modular logarithm and inverses, extended GCD, Farey series and continuous fractions. Includes Legendre and Jacobi symbols, some divisor functions, Euler's Phi function, etc.

name: r-numbers
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.7-5" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-numbers
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/numbers_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/numbers/numbers_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: ec3388eaedec7bdbf5a9a13e7697c0e1487d135b684e24b622dab62f6b1ee2b7

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('numbers')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('numbers')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=numbers
  license: GPL (>= 3)
  summary: ' Provides number-theoretic functions for factorization, prime  numbers, twin primes,
    primitive roots, modular logarithm and inverses, extended GCD, Farey series and
    continuous fractions. Includes Legendre and Jacobi symbols, some divisor functions,
    Euler''s Phi function, etc.'
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
